		<p></p>
		<h3>one.</h3>
		<p>A Good Sales Engineer is equally as good at selling a technology solution to the customer as they are at designing and implementing it.</p>
		<p></p>
		<h3>two.</h3>
		<p>A Good Sales Engineer is smarter than you…</p>
		<p></p>
		<h3>three.</h3>
		<p>A Good Sales Engineer has the ability to uncover more opportunity in every account.</p>
		<p></p>
		<h3>four.</h3>
		<p>A Good Sales Engineer knows how to explain the complicated “deep dive” technical details in simple and easy to understand language.</p>
		<p></p>
		<h3>five.</h3>
		<p>A Good Sales Engineer will know when you and the customer are looking at the wrong solution and won’t be afraid to suggest the right solution.</p>
		<p></p>
		</center>
	</marquee>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-3">
</div>	





<script>
	function toggle() {

			var ele = document.getElementById("toggleText");
			var text = document.getElementById("displayText");

			if(ele.style.display == "block") 
			{
		    	ele.style.display = "none";

		  	}
			else {
				ele.style.display = "block";

			}
	}
</script>	
